{"type":"message","id":"fad9501a","parentId":"537bce12","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:16:20.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to respond with suggestions for low/no money options: free tiers, open source models, using free credits, etc. Must follow formatting: bullets, double line breaks. Also must check memory before answering? The user asks about money, not prior work, so memory search not strictly needed but we should still do it? The instruction: \"Before answering anything about prior work, decisions, dates, people, preferences, or todos: run memory_search\". This is not about prior work etc, so we can skip. However safe to do a quick search? Not needed. We'll just answer.\n\nWe need to output with double line breaks after each bullet. Use bullets. Provide","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"• Use Hugging Face"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":" concise answer.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"’s free inference API – many models offer limited free calls each month  \n• Look for promotional credits:  \n  – Hugging Face sometimes gives $5‑$10 free inference credits for new accounts  \n  – Replicate and Together AI have free tiers or trial credits  \n• Quantize models to GGUF/4‑bit so they run on a laptop or cheap VPS (e.g., a $5/month cloud instance)  \n• Use Google Colab’s free GPU tiers (limited but sufficient for small experiments)  \n• Join open‑model communities (e.g., EleutherAI, LAION) that share free hosted APIs or volunteer‑run backends  \n• Start with very small models (1‑3B parameters) – they’re capable for many prompting tasks and need almost no GPU power  \n• Trade skills for compute: offer to help someone with prompting or agent setup in exchange for GPU hours on their spare rig  \n\n**Bottom line:** You can keep experimenting and building with zero‑to‑low cost by combining free tiers, model quantization, and community resources. Let me know if you want a step‑by‑step guide for any of these options."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":30018,"output":393,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30411,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774782948845,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b456d00b9c01a95e"}}
