{"type":"message","id":"5861f902","parentId":"b33cc6f6","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:19:09.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We are back on Nemotron with low reasoning effort as requested. Let's provide a concise, formatted response about the AI digest idea. We'll follow the formatting rules: bullets, double line breaks, headers where needed. We'll give a quick next-step plan.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**AI Daily Digest – Quick Start Plan**\n\n• **Core idea:**  \n  – Send a short AI news/learning digest via Telegram each morning  \n  – Content sourced from Hugging Face blog + arXiv cs.LG highlights  \n  – Store/archive in Notion for search and reference  \n\n• **MVP format (per message):**  \n  ```\n  **AI Daily Digest – YYYY‑MM‑DD**\n\n  • [Source] – Headline  \n    – One‑sentence summary  \n    – Why it matters to a builder  \n\n  • [Source] – Headline  \n    – One‑sentence summary  \n    – Why it matters  \n\n  • [Source] – Headline  \n    – One‑sentence summary  \n    – Why it matters  \n\n  **Quick try:** [One tiny prompt or code snippet to experiment with today]  \n\n  **Bottom line:** [One‑sentence takeaway]\n  ```\n\n• **Tech stack you already have:**  \n  – OpenClaw for fetching, summarizing, and sending Telegram messages  \n  – Notion API (you have the key) to store each digest item  \n  – cron or `/agent` to run the pipeline each morning  \n\n• **First‑step actions:**  \n  1. Create a Notion DB `Posts` (Date, Pillar, Title, Summary, Link, Tags)  \n  2. Write a simple script (or use OpenClaw’s `/agent`) that:  \n     – Fetches top item from Hugging Face blog  \n     – Fetches top arXiv cs.LG submission from the last day  \n     – Summarizes each in ≤2 sentences  \n     – Formats as bullets with double line breaks  \n     – Sends via `/message send --channel telegram --target <your_id> --message \"<formatted>\"`  \n     – Logs each item to Notion  \n  3. Test it manually today, then schedule for tomorrow morning  \n\n• **Monetization (later):**  \n  – Free tier: 3×/week digest  \n  – Premium ($3/month): daily + weekend deep‑dive + full archive access  \n\n**Bottom line:** Start with a manual test today, automate tomorrow, validate with friends, then layer on the paywall. Want me to draft the exact fetch‑and‑summarize command for one source now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":31636,"output":577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774783136465,"responseId":"chatcmpl-821fa4baf7dc1738"}}
