{"type":"message","id":"01302f19","parentId":"81641179","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:28:11.319Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4e7690a62ce24e4b944aea39","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"CLI tools for AI agents\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 928,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"eb3741847e0bdbb8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nbradAGI/awesome-cli-coding-agents - GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"eb3741847e0bdbb8\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/bradAGI/awesome-cli-coding-agents\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"778c9442e81b2498\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nA CLI coding agent is an AI -powered tool that runs in your terminal and can autonomously read, write, and execute code in your repository. Unlike chat-based assistants, these agents have direct access to your filesystem, shell, and dev tools — they can edit files, run tests, commit changes, and iterate on errors.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"778c9442e81b2498\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d4607fc5cb4f94ca\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n7 Best CLI AI Coding Agents in 2026 (Open Source)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d4607fc5cb4f94ca\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.scriptbyai.com/best-cli-ai-coding-agents/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea406289c9f6c2d2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nExplore 7 open-source CLI AI coding agents developers love in 2026. Tested by real users with GitHub data, features, and install guides.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea406289c9f6c2d2\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.scriptbyai.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82d3afea91c9be6c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe 2026 Guide to Coding CLI Tools: 15 AI Agents Compared\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82d3afea91c9be6c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.tembo.io/blog/coding-cli-tools-comparison\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e49d89a70a881953\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nA comprehensive comparison of 15 coding CLI tools—from Claude Code and Codex to Aider and Goose. We break down features, pricing, model support, and philosophy so you can pick the right terminal-based AI agent for your workflow.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e49d89a70a881953\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.tembo.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3f1622a518c6b18f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAgentic CLI Tools Compared: Claude Code vs Cline vs Aider\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3f1622a518c6b18f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://aimultiple.com/agentic-cli\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3ce57db9d696f65b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nExplore top free and open-source agentic CLI tools , such as Aider, Codex CLI , and Claude Code, for building and managing AI agents locally. These tools offer LLM integration, prompt chaining, and code editing capabilities, all within a terminal-based workflow.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3ce57db9d696f65b\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"aimultiple.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ff5bcc3f7df0a40d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCLI Is the New API and MCP: Building Agent-Ready Tools for Enterprise ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ff5bcc3f7df0a40d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://jonnyzzz.com/blog/2026/02/20/cli-tools-for-ai-agents/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"96cbcbfbf740110a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Agents already speak CLI . Better command UX is often the fastest path to enterprise agent integration.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"96cbcbfbf740110a\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"jonnyzzz.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"CLI tools for AI agents","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":928,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"eb3741847e0bdbb8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nbradAGI/awesome-cli-coding-agents - GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"eb3741847e0bdbb8\">>>","url":"https://github.com/bradAGI/awesome-cli-coding-agents","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"778c9442e81b2498\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nA CLI coding agent is an AI -powered tool that runs in your terminal and can autonomously read, write, and execute code in your repository. Unlike chat-based assistants, these agents have direct access to your filesystem, shell, and dev tools — they can edit files, run tests, commit changes, and iterate on errors.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"778c9442e81b2498\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d4607fc5cb4f94ca\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n7 Best CLI AI Coding Agents in 2026 (Open Source)\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"d4607fc5cb4f94ca\">>>","url":"https://www.scriptbyai.com/best-cli-ai-coding-agents/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ea406289c9f6c2d2\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nExplore 7 open-source CLI AI coding agents developers love in 2026. Tested by real users with GitHub data, features, and install guides.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"ea406289c9f6c2d2\">>>","siteName":"www.scriptbyai.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"82d3afea91c9be6c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe 2026 Guid