{"type":"message","id":"391e7f1a","parentId":"7f0b6cc6","timestamp":"2026-03-29T13:37:04.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to suggest passive income ideas based on prompt engineering / AI. Provide 3 ideas with double line breaks and bullet points. Should follow formatting. We'll produce bullet points with double line breaks after each bullet and","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"•"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":" after each section. Let's craft.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" **Sell Prompt Template Packs on Digital Marketplaces**  \n  – Create ready‑to‑use prompt bundles for popular niches (e.g., YouTube script writer, LinkedIn personal brand, SEO blog outlines, SQL query generator)  \n  – Host on Gumroad, Etsy, or Payhip with a one‑time price ($10‑$30) and automatic delivery  \n  – Once created, the product sells itself; you only need occasional updates or marketing  \n\n• **Build a Paid Prompt‑of‑the‑Week Newsletter (Substack/Beehiiv)**  \n  – Weekly email delivers a single high‑impact prompt, a short “why it works” breakdown, and a variation for different tones  \n  – Free tier gets a monthly digest; paid tier ($5/mo or $50/yr) gets full weekly prompts, searchable archive, and access to a private Discord for feedback  \n  – After the initial setup, revenue is recurring with minimal ongoing work (just curate and send)  \n\n• **License Your Prompt Library to AI‑Tool Platforms**  \n  – Package a collection of optimized prompts for specific models (GLM‑5, Nemotron, Claude, etc.) and offer them as an add‑on or plugin  \n  – Partner with platforms like PromptLayer, PromptHero, or model providers; earn a royalty per download or a flat licensing fee  \n  – This creates passive income as the platform handles distribution and you collect royalties over time  \n\n**Bottom line:** Focus on creating high‑quality, reusable digital assets once, then let them generate income through sales, subscriptions, or licensing with little ongoing effort. Pick one to prototype first and we can outline the exact steps."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":95566,"output":427,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774791382872,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a3a1381f0fdbceed"}}
