{"type":"message","id":"b417b7e4","parentId":"df42e792","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:30:52.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The transcript extraction is taking a while. Let me try getting video details first which is faster:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-8b8b756f595d5a9c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/ivo/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/youtube-research && python3 scripts/youtube_search.py --video E7fCvH-W61U --details"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":102735,"output":69,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774798208776,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8ad547f4064f8a17"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3dd60f82","parentId":"b417b7e4","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:30:52.708Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-8b8b756f595d5a9c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Master OpenClaw in 10 Hours [I Created 5 AI Employees]\n**URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E7fCvH-W61U\n**Channel:** Mani Kanasani\n**Published:** 2026-03-19\n**Duration:** 10:03:17\n\n## Statistics\n- Views: 69,409\n- Likes: 3,132\n- Comments: 278\n\n## Technical Details\n- Definition: HD\n- Dimension: 2d\n- Projection: rectangular\n- Has Captions: Yes\n- Licensed Content: Yes\n\n**Tags:** Claude Code, Claude Code Tutorial, AI SDR, AI Phone Agent, Discord Bot AI, AI Lead Generation, openclaw, openclaw tutorial, openclaw setup, OpenClaw\n\n## Description\nThe full source code and ClawBuddy app available in the community:\n🔗 https://join.verticalsystems.io/\n🔗 https://www.skool.com/aibox/about\n\nFREE setup guide: https://mani-k.kit.com/claw\n\nThe full OpenClaw masterclass — 10+ hours of building an autonomous AI agent system from scratch using Claude Code and Supabase.\n\nOpenClaw is an open-source mission control dashboard where AI agents manage your business operations. You'll build a Kanban board, sub-agents, cronjobs, Discord bots, and a multi-agent orchestration pipeline — all live.\n\nWhat you'll build in this OpenClaw tutorial:\n→ OpenClaw Setup & Installation — full configuration from zero\n→ Mission Control Dashboard — Kanban, AI logs, real-time agent status\n→ Sub Agents — specialized AI workers with token budgets\n→ Business Brain (3 levels) — memory architecture that makes agents smarter over time\n→ Meeting Intelligence — 1,650+ real transcripts powering auto-proposals\n→ AI Phone Agent — Voice AI for inbound, outbound, speed-to-lead\n→ AI SDR & Email Engine — scrape leads, personalize outreach, track everything\n→ AI Lead Generation — end-to-end pipeline from scrape to close\n→ Discord Bot AI — every agent gets its own bot, channel, and presence\n→ Cronjobs & Automations — polling, webhooks, heartbeats, Telegram alerts\n→ Multi-Agent Orchestration — two AI systems dispatching work to each other\n→ OpenClaw Credits & Claw Alley — AI agents transacting with each other on-chain (USDC on Base)\n\n⏱️ CHAPTERS\n0:00:00 Introduction\n0:18:47 Installation & Setup\n0:27:59 Sub-Agent Configuration\n0:34:59 Token Optimization\n0:58:05 Security\n1:21:47 Business Brain — Level 1\n1:24:24 Business Brain — Level 2 & 3\n1:32:22 Memory Architecture\n1:36:09 Mission Control Dashboard\n1:57:51 Integrations\n2:03:44 Task Management\n3:23:06 Builder, Orchestrator & Executor\n4:28:45 Business Operations Loop\n4:33:08 Meeting Intelligence\n5:50:46 Voice AI & Phone Agent\n6:23:20 Typeform Clone & Webhooks\n6:30:45 AI SDR & Email Engine\n8:13:27 Multi-Agent Orchestration\n8:38:09 Cronjobs & Automations\n8:55:02 Discord Integration\n9:10:15 Claw Alley — Agent-to-Agent Marketplace\n\n\nFREE Discovery Call: https://mani.wiki/discovery\n\nLet's Connect:\n=========================\nLinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/manikanasani/\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/manikanasanii\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/manikanasani/\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ManiKanasani\n\nTools I use: https://building-your-tech-stack-o5f3o8g.gamma.site/"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":349,"aggregated":"# Master OpenClaw in 10 Hours [I Created 5 AI Employees]\n**URL:** https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E7fCvH-W61U\n**Channel:** Mani Kanasani\n**Published:** 2026-03-19\n**Duration:** 10:03:17\n\n## Statistics\n- Views: 69,409\n- Likes: 3,132\n- Comments: 278\n\n## Technical Details\n- Definition: HD\n- Dimension: 2d\n- Projection: rectangular\n- Has Captions: Yes\n- Licensed Content: Yes\n\n**Tags:** Claude Code, Claude Code Tutorial, AI SDR, AI Phone Agent, Discord Bot AI, AI Lead Generation, openclaw, openclaw tutorial, openclaw setup, OpenClaw\n\n## Description\nThe full source code and ClawBuddy app available in the community:\n🔗 https://join.verticalsystems.io/\n🔗 https://www.skool.com/aibox/about\n\nFREE setup guide: https://mani-k.kit.com/claw\n\nThe full OpenClaw masterclass — 10+ hours of building an autonomous AI agent system from scratch using Claude Code and Supabase.\n\nOpenClaw is an open-source mission control dashboard where AI agents manage your business operations. You'll build a Kanban board, sub-agents, cronjobs, Discord bots, and a multi-agent orchestration pipeline — all live.\n\nWhat you'll build in this OpenClaw tutorial:\n→ OpenClaw Setup & Installation — full configuration from zero\n→ Mission Control Dashboard — Kanban, AI logs, real-time agent status\n→ Sub Agents — specialized AI workers with token budgets\n→ Business Brain (3 levels) — memory architecture that makes agents smarter over time\n→ Meeting Intelligence — 1,650+ real transcripts powering auto-proposals\n→ AI Phone Agent — Voice AI for inbound, outbound, speed-to-lead\n→ AI SDR & Email Engine — scrape leads, personalize outreach, track everything\n→ AI Lead Generation — end-to-end pipeline from scrape to close\n→ Discord Bot AI — every agent gets its own bot, channel, and presence\n→ Cronjobs & Automations — polling, webhooks, heartbeats, Telegram alerts\n→ Multi-Agent Orchestration — two AI systems dispatching work to each other\n→ OpenClaw Credits & Claw Alley — AI agents transacting with each other on-chain (USDC on Base)\n\n⏱️ CHAPTERS\n0:00:00 Introduction\n0:18:47 Installation & Setup\n0:27:59 Sub-Agent Configuration\n0:34:59 Token Optimization\n0:58:05 Security\n1:21:47 Business Brain — Level 1\n1:24:24 Business Brain — Level 2 & 3\n1:32:22 Memory Architecture\n1:36:09 Mission Control Dashboard\n1:57:51 Integrations\n2:03:44 Task Management\n3:23:06 Builder, Orchestrator & Executor\n4:28:45 Business Operations Loop\n4:33:08 Meeting Intelligence\n5:50:46 Voice AI & Phone Agent\n6:23:20 Typeform Clone & Webhooks\n6:30:45 AI SDR & Email Engine\n8:13:27 Multi-Agent Orchestration\n8:38:09 Cronjobs & Automations\n8:55:02 Discord Integration\n9:10:15 Claw Alley — Agent-to-Agent Marketplace\n\n\nFREE Discovery Call: https://mani.wiki/discovery\n\nLet's Connect:\n=========================\nLinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/manikanasani/\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/manikanasanii\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/manikanasani/\nYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@ManiKanasani\n\nTools I use: https://building-your-tech-stack-o5f3o8g.gamma.site/","cwd":"/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774798252697}}
