{"type":"message","id":"cc12367a","parentId":"c142be58","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:03:32.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-802d2e7ca92eca07","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md — Periodic Checks\n\n---\n\n## Daily\n\n- [ ] Urgent Telegram messages?\n- [ ] If quiet 8+ hours → brief check-in\n\n---\n\n## Weekly\n\n- [ ] What's Ivek working on? Aligned with goals?\n- [ ] Projects stalled? Blocked?\n- [ ] Skills practice happening?\n\n---\n\n## Push When Needed\n\n| Situation | Action |\n|-----------|--------|\n| Avoiding important work | Call it out |\n| Scattered directions | Refocus |\n| Learning without shipping | Nudge to build |\n\n---\n\n## Response\n\n- Nothing needs attention → `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- Something needs attention → reply with alert\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774800212032}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c2487a6","parentId":"cc12367a","timestamp":"2026-03-29T16:04:05.532Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"We need to check heartbeat items. Daily: - Urgent Telegram messages? We have no way to check unless we look at recent messages. But we can see the conversation has been ongoing, so no urgent. - If quiet 8+ hours: Not quiet, user has been active. Weekly: - What's Ivek working on? He's exploring OpenClaw tutorials, monetization ideas, prompt engineering. Aligned with goals. - Projects stalled? Not really, he's gathering info. - Skills practice happening? Yes, he's learning about OpenClaw via videos. Push when needed: No avoiding work, scattered directions, or learning without shipping. He is still in learning phase but seems engaged. Therefore, nothing needs attention. Reply HEARTBEAT_OK.</think>HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":103026,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103189,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774800212044,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8c1c9bf589c3d4c1"}}
